summary: This document is an email from the Chambers of Judge Alison J. Nathan transmitting the August 13 Opinion & Order and related motion papers in the case United States v. Maxwell (20cr330). It serves as a notification to counsel regarding the court's filings.

keyFacts: The communication is related to the criminal case United States v. Maxwell, docket number 20cr330.
The email transmits an August 13, 2021 Opinion & Order and related motion papers from Judge Alison J. Nathan's chambers.
The document is a procedural notification to counsel, confirming the court has issued new filings in the ongoing case.
